                     <interp inst="t17740706-41-off206" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a silver watch, value 2 l. a brass key, value 2 d. a steel chain, value 4 d. two silver table spoons, value 12 s. five silver tea spoons, value 10 s. a blue silk gown, value 15 s. a cotton gown, value 6 s. a black silk gown, value 21 s. a black silk hat, value 5 s. a pair of green silk shoes, value 5 s. a linen shift, value 3 s. a damask tablecloth, value 3 s. a shirt body, value 6 s. a linen sheet, value 10 s. two muslin aprons, value 21 s. and three cloth aprons, value 12 s. the property of 
                     
